          <summary>Why doesn't ChatGPT mention my brand?</summary>
          <div class="faq-answer"><p>ChatGPT relies on patterns from its training data and real-time browsing sources. If your brand lacks structured data, has thin third-party mentions, or doesn't appear on the sites ChatGPT references, it simply won't have enough signal to recommend you. Most businesses have near-zero ChatGPT visibility without deliberate optimisation.</p></div>
